videos.description: Tennessee comes out hot and puts up the first 14 points of the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Tennessee starts game out on a 14-0 run) 2022/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tennessee starts game out on a 14-0 run

videos.description: Texas A&M tries to get back in the game as Henry Coleman III works hard on the offensive glass for the and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Coleman works hard on the offensive glass for the and-1 in traffic) 2022/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coleman works hard on the offensive glass for the and-1 in traffic

videos.description: Santiago Vescovi picks off the in-bounds pass, then finds himself open for a 3-pointer and splashes it.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Vescovi does it all with the steal and a 3) 2022/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vescovi does it all with the steal and a 3

videos.description: Tennessee moves the ball flawlessly with Josiah-Jordan James finishing the play with a 2-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Excellent Tennessee passing leads to the James dunk) 2022/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Excellent Tennessee passing leads to the James dunk

videos.description: John Fulkerson comes down the lane and flushes home the huge two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Fulkerson skies for monster jam) 2022/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fulkerson skies for monster jam

videos.description: Marty Smith has his ears raised as he listens closely to the Tennessee huddle.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Marty Smith listens intently to the Tennessee huddle) 2022/03/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Marty Smith listens intently to the Tennessee huddle

videos.description: Tennessee starts out hot and never looks back as they beat Texas A&M and take home the SEC tournament title.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Tennessee takes down Texas A&M to win the SEC title) 2022/03/13 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Tennessee takes down Texas A&M to win the SEC title

videos.description: Rick Barnes keeps it short and sweet while reacting to Tennessee's first SEC Tournament victory since 1979.
videos.headline: Barnes has simple message following SEC title victory
